  june 14 , 1963 ( friday ) valery bykovsky was launched into orbit by the soviet union on board vostok 5."another russian man hurdles through space " , miami news , june 14 , 1963 , p1 bykovsky would spend almost five days in space ,   breaking the record recently set by american astronaut gordon cooper , and making 82 orbits before returning on june 19 , at the same time as vostok 6 and valentina tereshkova .

space exploration : in june 1963 she orbited 48 times in 70 hours , 50 minutes

